Subject: [PATCH v5 12/19] KVM: Move memslot deletion to helper function
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 2020 14:31:50 -0800
Message-Id: <20200121223157.15263-13-sean.j.christopherson@intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.24.1
